            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Even after changing `EslintFixAll` to `LspEslintFixAll`, it still doesn’t work. It seems the user’s on_attach function is overriding the default on_attach from lspconfig.\n\nrelated to https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/33577\n```lua\n  -- this works\n  local base_on_attach = vim.lsp.config.eslint.on_attach\n  vim.lsp.config('eslint', {\n    on_attach = function(client, bufnr)\n      base_on_attach(client)\n      vim.api.nvim_create_autocmd(\"BufWritePre\", {\n        buffer = bufnr,\n        command = \"LspEslintFixAll\",\n      })\n    end,\n  })\n```",
